This paper discusses the integration of femtocells into macrocell networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication protocols. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses quality of service provisioning, which is related to information theory and communication systems, making cs.IT (Information Theory) another likely category. The paper also mentions interference management and handover control, which are topics related to multimedia systems and signal processing, making cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible category. The paper also discusses the administrative challenges of network evolution, which is related to system and control theory, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category. Finally, the paper discusses security issues related to the integration of femtocells, which is a topic related to cryptography and security, making cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) a possible category.
